window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Miller </b></p> <p>They called me the pretty boy on and off the ice. Hockey’s most eligible bachelor. </p> <p>When my teammate asked me to donate one date to his charity, I figured why not. Worst case, I’d spend the night with a fan. Best-case scenario, she would be hot. What I wasn’t expecting was for my dream girl to be the highest bidder. </p> <p>For years, she brushed me off, and now, I finally had a chance to take her out and show her who I really was. </p> <p>With only one shot at this, I really hoped I didn’t mess it up. </p> <p><b>Layla </b></p> <p>At the top of my career, I was riding the wave of my sports talk show having the best rating on the radio. </p> <p>I also made it a rule to never date any sports players. </p> <p>It was my one rule, and I was sticking to it until I bid on the only man who gets under my skin.</p>"; 
